```rst
Usage
*****

Quickstart
==========

.. code-block:: bash

    pipx install hermesbaby
    hermesbaby new MyNewProject
    cd MyNewProject
    hermesbaby preview
    # Start editing ./docs/index.rst ...
```


```rst
See what's possible
===================

.. code-block:: bash

    cd
    hermesbaby new SeeWhatsPossible --template showcase
    cd SeeWhatsPossible
    hermesbaby preview
    # Investigate preview in browser and sources in editor
```

